21static inline isc_result_t
22generic_fromtext_tlsa(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24
25 UNUSED(type);
26 UNUSED(rdclass);
27 UNUSED(origin);
28 UNUSED(options);
29 UNUSED(callbacks);
30
31 /*
32 * Certificate Usage.
33 */
34 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
35 false));
36 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
37 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
38 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
39
40 /*
41 * Selector.
42 */
43 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
44 false));
45 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
46 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
47 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
48
49 /*
50 * Matching type.
51 */
52 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
53 false));
54 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
55 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
56 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
57
58 /*
59 * Certificate Association Data.
60 */
61 return (isc_hex_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
62}
63
64static inline isc_result_t
65generic_totext_tlsa(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
66 isc_region_t sr;
67 char buf[sizeof("64000 ")];
68 unsigned int n;
69
70 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
71
72 UNUSED(tctx);
73
74 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
75
76 /*
77 * Certificate Usage.
78 */
79 n = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
80 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
81 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", n);
82 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
83
84 /*
85 * Selector.
86 */
87 n = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
88 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
89 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u ", n);
90 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
91
92 /*
93 * Matching type.
94 */
95 n = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
96 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
97 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", n);
98 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
99
100 /*
101 * Certificate Association Data.
102 */
103 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
104 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
105 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
106 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
107 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&sr, 0, "", target));
108 else
109 RETERR(isc_hex_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
110 tctx->linebreak, target));
111 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
112 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
113 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
114}

116static inline isc_result_t
117generic_fromwire_tlsa(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
118 isc_region_t sr;
119
120 UNUSED(type);
121 UNUSED(rdclass);
122 UNUSED(dctx);
123 UNUSED(options);
124
125 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
126
127 if (sr.length < 3)
128 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
129
130 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
131 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
132}
133
134static inline isc_result_t
135fromtext_tlsa(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
136
137 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tlsa);
138
139 return (generic_fromtext_tlsa(rdclass, type, lexer, origin, options,
140 target, callbacks));
141}

160static inline isc_result_t
161towire_tlsa(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
162 isc_region_t sr;
163
164 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tlsa);
165 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
166
167 UNUSED(cctx);
168
169 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
170 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));

173static inline int
174compare_tlsa(ARGS_COMPARE) {
175 isc_region_t r1;
176 isc_region_t r2;
177
178 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
179 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
180 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_tlsa);
181 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
182 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
183
184 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
185 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
186 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
187}
188
189static inline isc_result_t
190generic_fromstruct_tlsa(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
191 dns_rdata_tlsa_t *tlsa = source;
192
193 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
194 REQUIRE(tlsa->common.rdtype == type);
195 REQUIRE(tlsa->common.rdclass == rdclass);
196
197 UNUSED(type);
198 UNUSED(rdclass);
199
200 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(tlsa->usage, target));
201 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(tlsa->selector, target));
202 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(tlsa->match, target));
203
204 return (mem_tobuffer(target, tlsa->data, tlsa->length));
205}
206
207static inline isc_result_t
208generic_tostruct_tlsa(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
209 dns_rdata_tlsa_t *tlsa = target;
210 isc_region_t region;
211
212 REQUIRE(rdata != NULL);
213 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
214
215 REQUIRE(tlsa != NULL);
216 REQUIRE(tlsa->common.rdclass == rdata->rdclass);
217 REQUIRE(tlsa->common.rdtype == rdata->type);
218 REQUIRE(!ISC_LINK_LINKED(&tlsa->common, link));
219
220 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
221
222 tlsa->usage = uint8_fromregion(&region);
223 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
224 tlsa->selector = uint8_fromregion(&region);
225 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
226 tlsa->match = uint8_fromregion(&region);
227 isc_region_consume(&region, 1);
228 tlsa->length = region.length;
229
230 tlsa->data = mem_maybedup(mctx, region.base, region.length);
231 if (tlsa->data == NULL)
232 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
233
234 tlsa->mctx = mctx;
235 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
236}
237
238static inline void
239generic_freestruct_tlsa(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
240 dns_rdata_tlsa_t *tlsa = source;
241
242 REQUIRE(tlsa != NULL);
243
244 if (tlsa->mctx == NULL)
245 return;
246
247 if (tlsa->data != NULL)
248 isc_mem_free(tlsa->mctx, tlsa->data);
249 tlsa->mctx = NULL;
250}
251
252static inline isc_result_t
253fromstruct_tlsa(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
254
255 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_tlsa);
256
257 return (generic_fromstruct_tlsa(rdclass, type, source, target));
258}
259
260static inline isc_result_t
261tostruct_tlsa(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
262 dns_rdata_tlsa_t *tlsa = target;
263
264 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tlsa);
265 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
266
267 tlsa->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
268 tlsa->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
269 ISC_LINK_INIT(&tlsa->common, link);
270
271 return (generic_tostruct_tlsa(rdata, target, mctx));
272}
273
274static inline void
275freestruct_tlsa(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
276 dns_rdata_tlsa_t *tlsa = source;
277
278 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
279 REQUIRE(tlsa->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_tlsa);
280
281 generic_freestruct_tlsa(source);
282}

295static inline isc_result_t
296digest_tlsa(ARGS_DIGEST) {
297 isc_region_t r;
298
299 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_tlsa);
300
301 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
302
303 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
304}
